data.description: SELLERS ARE OFFERING $5,000 TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COSTS OR BUY DOWN POINTS **NEW ROOF** to be installed prior to closing. NEW electric panel, Updated plumbing, A/C 2018, and Updated Kitchen! This property is centrally located right off of Atlantic Blvd. As you pull up to the home you will notice an extra large driveway with a one car garage. There is authentic hardwood flooring throughout, no carpet, and the kitchen sink has a window to overlook your backyard with beautiful oak trees. Love to watch the Jacksonville Jaguars then you will be a short 15 minute drive to downtown Jax only 10 minutes to San Marco and 20 to the beaches. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home YOURS!
